videos.headline: Mizzou RB explodes through hole for 27-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri running back Larry Rountree III gets the hand off and flies upfield for a 27-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Mizzou RB waltzes into end zone
videos.description: Missouri running back Damarea Crockett gets the toss and strolls in for the easy 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Franks muscles way into end zone
videos.description: Florida quarterback Feleipe Franks uses his size to push into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Mizzou WR taunts Florida fans after TD
videos.description: Missouri WR Kam Scott hauls in a 41-yard touchdown and does the gator chomp in the direction of the crowd to celebrate.

videos.headline: Lock fires TD pass, extending Mizzou's lead
videos.description: Drew Lock throws a dart to Emanuel Hall for the 4-yard touchdown extending Missouri's lead.

videos.headline: Florida's backup QB throws TD pass
videos.description: After replacing Feleipe Franks, Kyle Trask throws a 7-yard touchdown pass to Josh Hammond.

videos.headline: Lock throws 3 TDs and rises SEC history books
videos.description: Drew Lock throws three touchdowns in Missouri's big win over Florida, reaching 90 for his career.
